        "created_at": "2024-08-09T00:56:43.673Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Also, as I mentioned clicking on a notification is a little annoying because I need to manually click on the message box before typing. I can now 100% confirm this happens in both GNOME and KDE Plasma. Im not sure about other systems/desktops, but Im sure this is a widespread issue. I just thought I should bring up what specific systems it happens on as its been annoying me today and I thought it might only happen on specific environments.</p>",
